	<!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
	<!--
		Simple Design System — IconButton Styles (targeting Button)
		Maps SDS IconButton component to WinUI Button with circular shape.
		
		SDS IconButton: inherits all Button variant tokens,
		overrides border-radius to radius-full (9999px) and uses square aspect ratio.
		
		Variants: Primary, Neutral, Subtle, DangerPrimary, DangerSubtle
		Sizing:   Controlled by Space scale (DefaultSpacing) and SimpleIconLarge token
	-->

	<!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
